chance, and it looks like it uses cookies, or some other form of session
management to arrive at the page.

Directions:
Go to http://sourceforge.net/cvs/?group_id=15278 (this link does work to
the best of my knowledge)
In the sidebar to the right you will see the link to browse the CVS
repository. This is a web client to CVS. I guess you can take it from
there.
